OL,3,CWhistle-blowers raise concerns over
OL,4,Cpatient safety at hospital
OL,6,FThe Royal College of Nursing NI was
OL,7,Fdue to hold a webinar with members on
OL,8,FTuesday evening to discuss concerns
OL,9,Fmembers have about safety of patients
OL,10,Fbeing treated on corridors.
OL,12,FThe RCN's Rita Devlin said that the
OL,13,Fnumber of concerns raised with health
OL,14,Ftrusts through the whistleblowing
OL,15,Fpolicy is only the tip of the iceberg.
OL,17,FInformation received by UTV shows that
OL,18,F22 formal concerns were raised by
OL,19,Fhealth staff at the Belfast Health
OL,20,FTrust in the past year.
