OL,3,CWhistle-blowers raise concerns over
OL,4,Cpatient safety at hospital
OL,6,FWhile the majority related to the
OL,7,FRoyal Victoria Hospital, others
OL,8,Frelated to nursing homes, Belfast City
OL,9,FHospital, emergency social work and a
OL,10,Fmental health facility.
OL,12,FThe concerns included unsafe staffing
OL,13,Flevels, bed shortages, boarding of
OL,14,Fpatients, ED overcrowding, alleged
OL,15,Fdrug dealing on a hospital site, staff
OL,16,Fsleeping on night duty, lack of mental
OL,17,Fhealth beds and the quality of staff
OL,18,Ftraining.
