OL,3,CWhistle-blowers raise concerns over
OL,4,Cpatient safety at hospital
OL,6,FThe Belfast Trust said all staff are
OL,7,Fencouraged to make management aware of
OL,8,Fissues giving them concern through the
OL,9,Fwhistleblowing process.
OL,11,FThe Trust added: "Any concern we
OL,12,Freceive is subject to a fair and
OL,13,Fproportionate process of investigation.
OL,15,F"Whistleblowing investigations are of
OL,16,Fa fact finding nature and all relevant
OL,17,Flearning is shared as appropriate and
OL,18,Ftaken forward by the Trust.
OL,20,F"Every case is determined on its own
OL,21,Fmerits."
